<title>USA: Uno Restaurant names Miller to CEO post.</title>
<headline>Uno Restaurant names Miller to CEO post.</headline>
<dateline>BOSTON 1996-08-27</dateline>
<text>
<p>Uno Restaurant Corp said on Tuesday it named Craig Miller, the company's president and chief operating officer, to the additional post of chief executive, effective Sept. 30.</p>
<p>He will succeed Aaron Spencer in the post. Spencer will remain chairman.</p>
<p>Miller has served as Uno's president and chief operating officer since 1986.</p>
